cs.NI, cs.CY, cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.IT 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a communication framework for EV charging management. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper is motivated by the goal of reducing CO2 pollution. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper proposes a scheme for managing the charging of EVs. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is relevant as the paper proposes a distributed communication framework utilizing RSUs. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper proposes two complementary communication modes and analyzes their performance.
